Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要徹底收拾這些狗屎們
