Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也過來 快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂小鬼頭 我一個人出去 有人從洞口出來就開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 在找到Hiroshi之前我都和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:16:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前可別死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！ 糟了！ 糟了！
