Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Satoshi Batista 糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這車是防彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 是防彈車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 賞個臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 能堅持10分鐘的話我就饒了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話一定能辦到 準沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是真心的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要堅持5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來吧 你的話不是能辦到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke 你搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,88號公路請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在距離Goinia 15公里 國道交匯處正在封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 你可以下車了
