Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和情報不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goinia 只可能在那里
